---
title: Rustic Mushroom & Mixed Mash Pie with Veggies & Golden Panko Topping
description: A mushroom pie, you can find them in any bakery but we think this one has a special touch above the rest - it’s
made by you! A tomato sauce mushroom filling goes the extra mile with veggie additions like leek and carrot to
pack this pie up with a perfect ribbon.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
